{"tid":190782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做乜歧視D讀緊幼稚園既曳細佬?","createTime":"2017-04-07T10:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T23:53:51.000Z","uid":45142,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"889ca82c5e9402572f9784ba800c3944d2d8f9eb","tid":190782,"uid":45142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的，老人家冇啦啦拿返舊事黎講，唔講我都唔記得。<br />\n<br />\n我讀緊幼稚園既時候好撚曳，成日周圍跑黎跑去，跳黎跳去。有日姑婆搞家庭聚會，同我爺爺講唔好帶我同我老媽子去，驚我失禮。我屌你老母，我爺爺真係唔撚帶我去，佢帶左我堂哥同堂弟去，呢兩條友真係好撚乖好撚靜，仲好似好好學，成日拿書刨。<br />\n<br />\n我失禮咩？我會周圍柯屎柯屎？我會拿屎扔你咩？我會亂咁偷野，斬人咩？我只不過係貪玩好動，基本野我都係識既。我冇拿住本書刨係唔係好撚失禮你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n姑婆走左，我都冇去到葬禮，我驚失禮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以家Ｄ老人家問我野，我都hea 9佢地。（Model answer : 哦，嗯，我唔知）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：讀緊Ｕ，其他２條友ＨＤ中。"},{"pid":"9026881fb0c51ba4a5885d43ead7e1ac50bd9355","tid":190782,"uid":45142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e9d5cfe9ddbb1a741359a44a1798b7821b89ab2","tid":190782,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4f3500ef2acef431bb3a383c7a76001d7356643","tid":190782,"uid":45142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:25:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/133932/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/133932/page/1</a> 樓主好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係廢J"},